{"type":"message","id":"8900ac6b","parentId":"67d230f0","timestamp":"2026-04-14T02:45:24.988Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-14 02:45:23 UTC] Summarize latest AI news from last 24 hours.\nSystem: \nSystem: Focus on:\nSystem: - LLMs\nSystem: - RL\nSystem: - Diffusion models\nSystem: - VLM / robotics\nSystem: \nSystem: Output:\nSystem: - 5 bullet points\nSystem: - Why it matters (2 lines)\n\nA scheduled reminder has been triggered. The reminder content is:\n\nSummarize latest AI news from last 24 hours.\n\nFocus on:\n- LLMs\n- RL\n- Diffusion models\n- VLM / robotics\n\nOutput:\n- 5 bullet points\n- Why it matters (2 lines)\n\nHandle this reminder internally. Do not relay it to the user unless explicitly requested.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 — 2:45 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-14 02:45 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776134724981}}
{"type":"message","id":"3f0af0c7","parentId":"8900ac6b","timestamp":"2026-04-14T02:45:59.820Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_64f64619-d21f-44fd-a353-ca86ea70bbfb","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"latest AI news from last 24 hours LLMs RL Diffusion models VLM robotics","count":5}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"qwen-local:latest","usage":{"input":8057,"output":44,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":8101,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1776134759813}}
{"type":"message","id":"96e66fe5","parentId":"3f0af0c7","timestamp":"2026-04-14T02:45:59.904Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_64f64619-d21f-44fd-a353-ca86ea70bbfb","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"error\": \"missing_brave_api_key\",\n  \"message\": \"web_search (brave) needs a Brave Search API key. Run `openclaw configure --section web` to store it, or set BRAVE_API_KEY in the Gateway environment.\",\n  \"docs\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web\"\n}"}],"details":{"error":"missing_brave_api_key","message":"web_search (brave) needs a Brave Search API key. Run `openclaw configure --section web` to store it, or set BRAVE_API_KEY in the Gateway environment.","docs":"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776134759902}}
{"type":"message","id":"bb67f026","parentId":"96e66fe5","timestamp":"2026-04-14T02:46:30.935Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"It seems that I don't have a search API key configured for browsing the internet through Brave. To retrieve information like recent AI news from the web, OpenClaw relies on an API key provided by Brave.\n\nTo resolve this issue, you can configure it using the following steps:\n1. Use the command `openclaw configure --section web` to store a key in your environment.\n2. Alternatively, set the variable **BRAVE_API_KEY** directly in your local Gateway configuration.\n\nOnce configured properly, I'll be able to fetch and summarize the latest AI news as requested. If you need further assistance with configuring Brave API keys or anything else, feel free to ask!\n"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"qwen-local:latest","usage":{"input":8186,"output":138,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":8324,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1776134790931}}
